data.eml:eml: Deep-sea ascidians from Papua New Guinea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Monniot, Françoise, López-Legentil, Susanna (2017): Deep-sea ascidians from Papua New Guinea. Zootaxa 4276 (4): 529-538, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4276.4.5
